    <item>
      <title>中国电动汽车的繁荣并没有填补房地产市场低迷带来的漏洞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/china-s-electric-car-boom-isn-t-filling-hole-from-housing-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的电动汽车行业正在蓬勃发展，去年销量猛增 35%，出口量也猛增。但这还不足以弥补长达数年的房地产业危机对经济增长的拖累。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/china-s-electric-car-boom-isn-t-filling-hole-from-housing-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 03:45:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南 FPT 预计到 2030 年海外销售额将跃升至 50 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/vietnam-s-fpt-sees-overseas-sales-jumping-to-5-billion-by-2030</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南最大的上市科技公司 FPT Corp. 董事长 Truong Gia Binh 表示，预计未来几年海外市场的总收入将成倍增长，到 2030 年将达到 50 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/vietnam-s-fpt-sees-overseas-sales-jumping-to-5-billion-by-2030</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 03:11:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Citadel 证券是瑞士信贷中国唯一的全球竞购者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/citadel-is-only-global-bidder-for-credit-suisse-s-china-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，Citadel Securities LLC 已对瑞士信贷在中国的证券业务提出了不具约束力的收购要约，成为唯一一家提交收购要约的全球金融公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/citadel-is-only-global-bidder-for-credit-suisse-s-china-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 00:34:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果与被指控“秘密”盗窃的初创公司关系缓和</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/apple-eyes-detente-with-startup-it-accused-of-stealth-theft</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司正在就其指控芯片初创公司 Rivos Inc. 挖角工程师窃取商业机密的指控进行和解谈判，并反诉该 iPhone 制造商强迫员工签署限制其工作地点的反竞争协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-11/apple-eyes-detente-with-startup-it-accused-of-stealth-theft</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jan 2024 00:02:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳斯达克利用人工智能技术投资打击金融犯罪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/nasdaq-invests-in-fighting-financial-crime-using-ai-technology</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳斯达克首席执行官阿迪娜·弗里德曼 (Adena Friedman) 表示，随着阻止复杂的不良行为者的需求不断增加，纳斯达克正在大力支持防范金融犯罪的技术。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/nasdaq-invests-in-fighting-financial-crime-using-ai-technology</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 23:54:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技公司的裁员让恢复快速增长的希望渺茫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/tech-layoffs-may-be-back-with-amazon-twitch-unity-duolingo-job-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科技行业的新的一年已经开始，多家公司宣布大幅裁员。这让人想起 2023 年是如何开始的，当时是十多年来最严重的行业萎缩之前。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/tech-layoffs-may-be-back-with-amazon-twitch-unity-duolingo-job-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 21:36:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技股的增长困境给印度股市的强劲上涨带来风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/tech-s-growth-woes-pose-a-risk-to-india-stocks-sizzling-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据估计，印度顶级科技公司的收入增长放缓，可能会阻碍该国股市的持续飙升，而印度股市是华尔街首选的新兴市场股票之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/tech-s-growth-woes-pose-a-risk-to-india-stocks-sizzling-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 09:31:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称李氏家族将出售价值 20 亿美元的三星股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/samsung-electronics-holder-seeks-up-to-1-65-billion-in-block</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，三星集团背后的李氏家族出售了四家首尔上市公司价值约 20 亿美元的股票。周四首尔早盘交易中，这四家公司的股价均下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/samsung-electronics-holder-seeks-up-to-1-65-billion-in-block</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 09:10:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SEC 帐户被盗加剧了有关 X 安全的问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/sec-s-compromised-account-amplifies-x-trust-security-concerns</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国证券交易委员会表示，其在社交网络 X 上的账户“遭到泄露”，导致比特币价格飙升，并引发了人们对 X 作为信息来源和用户安全选项的可靠性的新质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-10/sec-s-compromised-account-amplifies-x-trust-security-concerns</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jan 2024 00:56:56 GMT</pubDate>
